Subject: [PATCH 2352/5242] MLK-13975: ASoC: fsl: amix: fix maximum values

commit  e2b230a4e84578a2e8b87f1793ac5bc0f3fa9f42 from
https://source.codeaurora.org/external/imx/linux-imx.git

AMIX maximum values for attenuation initial value,
step up/down factors and step target is 0x3FFFFh.

Signed-off-by: Viorel Suman <viorel.suman@nxp.com>
Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
---
 sound/soc/fsl/fsl_amix.c |   20 ++++++++++----------
 1 file changed, 10 insertions(+), 10 deletions(-)

diff --git a/sound/soc/fsl/fsl_amix.c b/sound/soc/fsl/fsl_amix.c
index e9c0716..c13071c 100644
--- a/sound/soc/fsl/fsl_amix.c
+++ b/sound/soc/fsl/fsl_amix.c
@@ -63,28 +63,28 @@
